### 4. Finance Journey — Receipt to Record to Memory

Journey นี้ใช้กับ Finance Workspace

Flow:

```text id="plwou9"
Finance user uploads receipt/bill
→ OCR extracts fields
→ System suggests:
   - vendor
   - category
   - amount
   - VAT/tax fields
   - duplicate warning
→ User reviews and edits fields
→ Finance lead / department lead confirms
→ System creates finance record
→ Record links back to source receipt
→ Finance dashboard updates
→ Approved finance info becomes Work Memory
→ AI can answer finance questions with source
```

Rules:

```text id="y1dmew"
- AI/OCR cannot post finance records automatically
- Human confirmation is required
- Finance numbers must be calculated by deterministic code, not LLM guessing
- Finance records must cite source receipt/document
- Sensitive finance memory stays inside Finance unless approved as shared knowledge
```

UX principle:

```text id="b3fp4t"
Finance user should feel like the system reduces manual typing and helps prevent mistakes, not like AI is taking over accounting decisions
```

