### 6. AI Chat Journey — Ask with Sources and Permission

Journey นี้คือประสบการณ์ AI Chat หลักของ MindKeep

Flow:

```text id="sajg6s"
User opens AI Chat
→ Selects or confirms active department scope
→ Starts new chat or opens old chat
→ Asks question
→ System resolves user permissions
→ System retrieves:
   - shared_knowledge
   - approved Work Memory of allowed department
   - allowed source documents
→ AI answers with source citations
→ User opens cited source if needed
→ User can save useful answer as note or activity
```

Rules:

```text id="zj5b2q"
- Chat history must not disappear
- User can create new chat
- AI must cite sources when using company data
- AI must not search unauthorized departments
- AI must not expose hidden source content
- AI must say it cannot find accessible information if no allowed source exists
```

UX principle:

```text id="m5byx6"
AI Chat should feel familiar like ChatGPT, but safer because it only answers from company data that the user is allowed to access
```

